pursuant to this section on its website.\\par\n2. The department of parks and recreation shall provide the department with the written materials developed pursuant to this section. The department shall distribute such materials to each school, to be shared with every student of each school, at the beginning and end of each academic year. \\par\n\\ulnone\\'a7 2. This local law takes effect immediately.\\ul\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\noline\\qj\\ulnone\\fs18\\par\nDPM/KS\\par\nLS #17419\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\noline 11/25/25 5:10PM\\par\n\\par\n}\n",
